♬ Call it morning
driving through

325
00:22:24,159 --> 00:22:29,564
♬ the sound and
in and out the valley

326
00:22:29,564 --> 00:22:36,905
♬～

327
00:22:36,905 --> 00:22:40,508
♬ The music dance and sing

328
00:22:40,508 --> 00:22:44,179
♬ They make
the children really ring

329
00:22:44,179 --> 00:22:49,517
♬ Spend the day away

330
00:22:49,517 --> 00:22:51,186
♬ Call it morning
driving through

331
